cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically single-image dehazing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a neural network approach, which involves training the network to perform two tasks simultaneously, haze removal and transmission map estimation. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning techniques, which could place it in the cs.MM (Multimedia) category. Finally, the paper could also be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics) as it deals with image processing.
